  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1660_brd_ac_8_r.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
               <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">
                  <unclear>نوازش</unclear>
                  خان</persName>
               مرید حضرت محمد 
               <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">اورنگ زیب عالم گیر</persName>
               <unclear>باد</unclear>
               شاه غازی
               <num>۱۰۷۰</num>
            </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><persName ref="#nawazishKhan"><unclear>Nawazish</unclear> Khan</persName> disciple of Lord Muhammad <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">Aurangzeb Alamgir</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_badshah">[Bad]shah</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_ghazi">Ghazi</ref> <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1070</date><note>A very clear impression of the same seal is found on <ref type="document" target="#lf_pDas_1660_brd_ac_ii">Order of Nawazish Khan to Purshottam Das granting a house</ref>. Gaps in the reading of the seal impression are supplied through comparison.</note></mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>زبدة الاقران
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم</persName>
               چودری پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               بعنایت و مهربانی امیدوار
               <lb/>بوده بداند که درینولا بعرض رسید که حویلی که در ان
               <persName ref="#bulaqiChand">بولاقیچند</persName>
               می بود
               <lb/>متعلقه او است لهذا از روی عنایت حویلی مذکور باو مرحمت فرمودیم
               <lb/> باید که حویلی مزبور مسمار نموده چوب انچه باشد بحضور برساند و
               <lb/>بدستور سابق انجا را متصرف شود و بدولتخواهی و کفایت
               <lb/>سرکار مقید و سرگرم باشد درین باب نهایت
               <lb/>تاکید دانسته از
               <unclear>فرموده</unclear>
               تخلف نورزد تحریر فی التاریخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">
                  <num>۲۶</num>
                  دی حجه سنه 
                  <num>۱۰۷۰</num></date>
               <g ref="#faqt">فقط</g>
               <g ref="#faqt">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3">
            <p>
               <lb/>Eminent among Contemporaries
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam [Das]</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>
               , being hopeful of favour and kindness,
               <lb/>know that at this time it was petitioned that the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_haveli">haveli</ref> in which
               <persName ref="#bulaqiChand">Bulaqi Chand</persName>
                was [living],
               <lb/>belongs to him [i.e.,
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>
               ]. Therefore, by way of assistance, we ordered the aforesaid <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_haveli">haveli</ref> [to be] presented to him.
               <lb/>It is necessary that the aforesaid <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_haveli">haveli</ref> is torn down [and] however much wood there shall be, is sent to the
               Lord. And
               <lb/>according to past custom that place shall be taken into his possession and he
               shall be engaged and
               <lb/>occupied with loyalty towards and prosperity of the government. In this matter
               <lb/>knowing it firmly settled, do not neglect to do what is ordered. Written on the
               date
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">26 Zi al-hijja year 1070</date>
               .
               <g ref="#faqt">Nothing further.</g>
               <g ref="#faqt">Nothing further.</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="right margin">
            <p>هو</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4">
            <p>He [God] is</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p>حسب المسطور مقرر
               <unclear>شناسند</unclear>
               <g ref="#faqt">فقط</g></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div5" corresp="#orig_div5">
            <p><unclear>Know</unclear> it appointed as written. <g ref="#faqt">Nothing further.</g></p>
         </div>
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1660_brd_ac_8_v.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <lb/>نقل
               <unclear>سیاهه</unclear>
              <lb/>بتاریخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>۲۷</num>
               دی الحجه سنه 
                  <num>۱۰۷۰</num>
               </date>               
               <lb/>نقلدفتر دیوان
               <unclear>رسید</unclear>  
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div6" corresp="#orig_div6">
            <p>
               <lb/>Register copy
               <lb/>On the date <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">27 Zi al-hijja year 1070</date>
               <lb/>a copy reached the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_daftar">daftar</ref> of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_diwan">diwan</ref>.
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div7" xml:lang="per" type="laterAddition" rend="top right">
            <p>پروانه بنام چودری
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتمداس</persName>
               در باب معافی حویلی</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div7" corresp="#orig_div7">
            <p><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref> in the name of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> regarding a tax-exempt <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_haveli">haveli</ref></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div8" xml:lang="hin" type="laterAddition" rend="top left">
            <p>प्रवानो <choice><abbr>बा॰</abbr><expan><unclear>बाबत</unclear></expan></choice> माफ हवेली</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div8" corresp="#orig_div8">
            <p><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref> <unclear>regarding</unclear> a tax-free <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_haveli">haveli</ref></p>
         </div>
      </body>
  </text>
